								</svg>
								Science education receives priority protection from budget cuts
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								Laboratory facilities and equipment funding maintained
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								Enhanced career prospects for science graduates
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start">
								<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
									<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
								</svg>
								Long-term commitment to UK scientific excellence
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Related Articles -->
	<section class="py-16 bg-white">
		<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="text-center mb-12">
